OL,6,FA man who stabbed his partner to death
OL,7,Fin front of train station commuters
OL,8,Fhas been found guilty of murder.
OL,10,FIn August last year at Crawley train
OL,11,Fstation, Jason Flore, 26, stabbed 19-
OL,12,Fyear-old Stephanie Marie in the chest
OL,13,Fwith a knife, puncturing her heart.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,16,Fscene but paramedics were unable to
OL,17,Fsave Ms Marie.
