OL,3,CMan who stabbed girlfriend in chest in
OL,4,Crailway car park found guilty of murder
OL,6,FThe court heard how, on Sunday 18
OL,7,FAugust 2024, at around 7.05am, police
OL,8,Fwere called after Flore was seen
OL,9,Farguing with Stephanie in the train
OL,10,Fstation car park in Sussex.
OL,12,FFlore was described as being very
OL,13,Faggressive and waving his hands at
OL,14,FStephanie, who was undressed from the
OL,15,Fwaist down, visibly upset and
OL,16,Fdistressed, and in possession of a
OL,17,Fknife.
