OL,6,FThirteen minutes later, a separate 999
OL,7,Fcall was made calling for an
OL,8,Fambulance, reporting a woman `
OL,9,FStephanie ` had been stabbed.
OL,11,FThe caller stated she was not
OL,12,Fbreathing but that they needed to
OL,13,Fleave for their train. The number was
OL,14,Flater confirmed to belong to Flore.
OL,16,FFlore was located and stopped near
OL,17,FHaslett Avenue East, heading towards
OL,18,FThree Bridges railway station at 8am,
OL,19,Fat which point he told officers "She
OL,20,Fdid it to herself."
