OL,6,FHe was arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fattempted murder by armed officers
OL,8,Ffrom Sussex Police. However following
OL,9,FStephanie's death, Flore was arrested
OL,10,Ffor murder minutes later.
OL,12,FA jury took three hours and 40 minutes
OL,13,Fto find him guilty of murdering Ms
OL,14,FMarie.
OL,16,FStephanie Marie and Jason Flore, both
OL,17,Foriginally from Mauritius, were living
OL,18,Fin a makeshift tent camp at a disused
OL,19,Fstation car park.
