OL,4,Crailway car park found guilty of murder
OL,6,FFlore will be sentenced at Hove Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Thursday (20 February).
OL,9,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,10,FSuperintendent Sam Blackburn said:
OL,11,F"Stephanie was a young woman with a
OL,12,Fwhole life ahead of her to enjoy, but
OL,13,Fhad it stolen away by a controlling
OL,14,Fand coercive partner.
OL,16,F"She was a much loved daughter,
OL,17,Fsister, and mother who enjoyed sports,
OL,18,Fmusic ` especially playing guitar, and
OL,19,Fhad ambitions to be a hairdresser.
