OL,6,F"This outcome is the result of
OL,7,Fcountless hours of investigation and I
OL,8,Fthank everyone who has contributed to
OL,9,Fensuring Stephanie's killer has been
OL,10,Fheld accountable for what he did
OL,11,Ftoday. It is important that we
OL,12,Fremember her name today instead of his
OL,14,F"While today's verdict will never
OL,15,Freplace the tragic loss felt by those
OL,16,Fwho loved Stephanie, it has ensured
OL,17,Fthat justice has been served. I hope
OL,18,Fthis outcome helps them find some
OL,19,Fpeace after such a devastating loss."
